  "text": "In Keystroke logging an adversary covertly records user's keystroke as they are being typed either through a software program or a hardware device or even by monitoring electromagnetic emissions. Deployed through variety of methods, malware programmers often leverage software key loggers as a payload or a client-side exploit [CITATION_1] , [90] . Software based keystroke logging can be implemented in kernel, hypervisor or in memory.",
